  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">A right circular cylinder has a volume of <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"45 pi\"></span></span>. If the height of the cylinder is 5, what is the radius of the cylinder?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
